title: gals on the go 101: starting our podcast + what we have learned
itunes:title: gals on the go 101: starting our podcast + what we have learned
description:
Brooke and Danielle are talking all about how Gals on the Go began!  With so many people trying to get into podcasting in 2021, the gals are breaking down how they started in 2018.  Who thought of the original concept?  Who thought of the name?  What are the gals biggest tips to those trying to start a podcast?  The gals also catch up on their summer adventures and share what they have been up to!  


Learn More About Save Our Stages: https://www.saveourstages.com/ https://www.nivassoc.org/.
